Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee Chairman: Firmly believe that China has the ability to host a successful Winter Olympics during special times - Xinhua News Agency Xinhua News Agency, Sarajevo, December 11th - Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee Chairman Kvesic recently stated that Bosnia is looking forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics and firmly believes that China has the ability to host a successful Winter Olympics during special times. Chinese Ambassador to Bosnia and Herzegovina, Ji Ping, met with Kvesic at the Sarajevo Olympic Center. During the meeting, Kvesic positively commented on the relations between Bosnia and China and said that he visited China during the 2008 Beijing Summer Olympics and was deeply impressed by the outstanding organization work of the Chinese side. He firmly believes that China has the ability to host a successful Winter Olympics during special times. Bosnia is looking forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics, and the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee is actively organizing participation. Bosnia hopes to take this opportunity to carry out more extensive exchanges and cooperation with China in the field of sports. Ji Ping said that China and Bosnia and Herzegovina have a special "Olympic bond". In 1984, the Sarajevo Winter Olympics were successfully held here, and in two months, the 2022 Beijing Winter Olympics will also be unveiled, presenting a simple, safe, and splendid event to the world. It is expected that the two countries will deepen exchanges and cooperation in the preparation of winter sports events, athlete training, and other aspects. The Chinese Embassy in Bosnia and Herzegovina is willing to continue playing a bridging role, taking the Beijing Winter Olympics as an opportunity to promote the continuous deepening of cultural exchanges between the two countries and to let the people of both countries "move towards the future together." Best wishes to the Bosnian athletes for achieving excellent results in Beijing. Before the meeting, the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee held the "10th Annual Best Athlete" award ceremony. Ji Ping, as a special guest, presented the award to the best young athlete in Bosnia and Herzegovina. Promotional videos of the Beijing Winter Olympics were played in a loop at the event.
